Qaddafi Daughter Files War Crimes Claims Against NATO, AFP Says

-- B y   H e a t h e r   S m i t h
-- 
2011-06-07T16:51:06Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-07/qaddafi-daughter-files-war-crimes-claims-against-nato-afp-says.html
Libyan leader  Muammar Qaddafi ’s
daughter filed criminal complaints claiming the North Atlantic
Treaty Organization’s April 30 attack killing Qaddafi’s son and
three grandchildren constituted a war crime, Agence France-
Presse said today, citing her lawyers.  The complaints were filed to the Brussels public prosecutor
and the Belgian federal prosecutor, AFP said. The daughter who
filed the complaint was the mother of one of the grandchildren
killed in the attack, the  news agency  said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Heather Smith in Paris at 
 hsmith26@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Anthony Aarons at   aaarons@bloomberg.net . 